{"tid":1286940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［政治思維］政治係冷酷嘅計算 唔好做神 亦不必代表分化","createTime":"2019-07-05T04:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T06:27:16.000Z","uid":149630,"like":169,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a563ecf09eaf03160ff2b8eb0f11e61f50a4e987","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n呢句當年係邊班人高舉？<br />\n記得嘅話<br />\n就唔會將所有事都劃做私怨<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Anyway 我都認同現階段唔好嘈咁多</span></span><br />\n但大家嘅思維應該改變<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每個政治人物係畀大眾「利用」而唔係「支持」<br />\n分清莊閒，有必要時<br />\n甚至要狠狠唾棄<br />\n</span></span><br />\n例如周庭今次行動無問題，表現出色<br />\n之前嘅所作所為<br />\n係咪可以就此一筆勾銷<br />\n呢啲係今次戰役過後<br />\n可以容後再談<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政治需要冷酷計算<br />\n例如飯民就算今次單次表現好<br />\n唔代表根據過去現在<br />\n做出嘅綜合判斷<br />\n就必定要為單次功勞而贏到我嘅一票<br />\n<br />\n又例如立會當日<br />\n民眾需要有議員身份嘅人幫手<br />\n大家好似當左議員係物資咁<br />\n係周圍呼籲「煲底要議員」<br />\n當成可利用之物<br />\n係政治智力嘅萌芽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人有記性唔係罪過<br />\n記憶係對抗極權最重要嘅事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有人係度間中重提舊事<br />\n唔一定係咩所謂分化<br />\n而係話畀所有枱面人物聽<br />\nWe remember anything<br />\n你地時刻受住監察壓力<br />\n你地要醒醒定定</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時刻對政客保持懷疑同警惕<br />\n係基本嘅政治智慧<br />\n先係維持運動嘅動能同張力嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為左個運動<br />\n現階段<br />\n飯民蠢蠢欲動<br />\n反而最需要緊密監視<br />\n好好馴服利用嘅一群人</span></span>"},{"pid":"05bbc10698664683fb96b1e84067ec3d998c55c2","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15f49976380392531ec526b7e3adc28326aa5b06","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:22:02.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"a6746f60b7230b982c95d39d028a03718d14fcbb","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"fa52571bb97a88f4a401b3e79d79cf6938dfde8a","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:23:43.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"e56d76896a2eb746d9838eb7495bb44be3e52015","tid":1286940,"uid":255105,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"正確，除咗要監督泛民，都唔應該遺忘當年熱狗係點樣搞網絡清算。鄭松泰而家肯幫下手都唔代表啲咩，要緊密監視住佢地派系堆人"},{"pid":"14a06bfec81ad2246188d8aa1b2b9e61cfdd25a4","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:25:20.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"64688ec42c5e92913378e293df1701f5ca4fc963","tid":1286940,"uid":190930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"Well said.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d8557fcb0267bd4f87ecb79ddb54c54c56386f","tid":1286940,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n大家都係同路人<br />\n團結則贏<br />\n分化則輸"},{"pid":"4a279153d6cf3ad4e166aaf8a9ab7f8e35a86b2e","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"8c53536ac4b7d98e0ccaedf207ad133727eb49ab","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:31:04.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"fead928da86b500e89918be0d4722e728344f09b","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"72d897fddb2dbba59d52a1fcf095356620d2c014","tid":1286940,"uid":45160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"中肯"},{"pid":"2d802bb559ff06b8948dd5039f72f724d2828c27","tid":1286940,"uid":45160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:32:28.000Z","msg":"希望大家花啲時間睇睇<br />\n抗爭要贏 唔止要識點打 仲要識點諗 <br />\n(講思想基礎，思想同行動一樣重要，希望大家可以睇下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cQLGCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cQLGCS</a><br />\n[深度分析]民意與民心的分別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1253834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1253834</a><br />\n鄭立：專心抗爭，現在才是最危險的時候<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242198</a><br />\n［政治思維］政治係冷酷嘅計算 唔好做神 亦不必代表分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286940</a>"},{"pid":"e4d6381a9aa9a9faac58ebb7ca72da44b65aac78","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:32:30.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"f0b46a8c4ffc4181e68c9069ca16964ac239b35a","tid":1286940,"uid":267395,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"講得好 講到明 政治係爭取利益既工具 大家一定要識用"},{"pid":"6d5ebf773c1f261ef3aa9ef076cf680d0a02d62c","tid":1286940,"uid":164050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f82272a5dd5d8cd4628d0b712c35f552a1426289","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:36:21.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"7f388d5d7dea18dee7ecf750118bca11b7b3f803","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:37:14.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"3e289cfa30b714b1612b2c0a39f3af7fb89ba957","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"c4f7ed6b5f4909c606292a8f1782b2fc86245a17","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"我無話講"},{"pid":"7ad458607464368fd80fa13578a98720aab4874e","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"fdd5ce8c95fef7bbb2cf25ab45cbaacf7b0b0703","tid":1286940,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,